         By the way, that's NOT saying necros don't need help, too!  However, I have pocket necro, whom I adore, and I think he does a LOT for both groups AND raids, but, I imagine I'm a bit biased in regards to him... :)</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
